    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你来到了一个神秘的岛屿，在这里，你被变成了小孩的模样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里没有繁重的工作，只要快乐地生活就好，直到永远，永远……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，当你厌倦了这样的生活，你还能找到从这里离开的路吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏详情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将扮演一位初入永无乡的居民，开始在岛上度过休闲愉快的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/3facec9afb0558be2382d5793bf6d934.avif?t=1739514331\" width=660 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·探索岛屿的不同地点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/388d0c22951d695491df0a7b520092d4.avif?t=1739514331\" width=548 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·与个性鲜明的npc进行社交，根据情况，也有展开恋爱的可能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/363057b521816a667b45d0b440808b29.avif?t=1739514331\" width=494 height=420 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·种植农作物，收获果实</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/55f2d3708ed43489485dfbca2e5ccfd7.avif?t=1739514331\" width=786 height=330 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·制作美食，招待你的朋友</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/dda91b2dd9d46aba1241b9b51a6b5619.avif?t=1739514331\" width=800 height=264 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·参与节日，收集节日奖励</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/6545335005527ca02e36b85cb34976f0.avif?t=1739514331\" width=626 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·通过探索和推理寻找离开的方法，达成结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，岛上还隐藏着一系列秘密，等待你去揭开……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您有bug需要汇报，请加入群聊：254521470</p>",
